	* eval.c (ruby_finalize_0): return the given exit status unless
	  SystemExit got raised.

Tue Oct 14 11:53:49 2003  Nobuyoshi Nakada  <nobu@ruby-lang.org>

	* intern.h (ruby_stop): never return.

	* ruby.h (ruby_run): ditto.

